### Audio Visualizer

An audio visualizer with FFT spectral analysis and custom shader rendering.

[Watch](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bYk8sEuPvlk) it or [browse](https://github.com/agilul/audio-visualization) the source code.

### Love2D Demos

Software renderer. [[Source](https://github.com/agilul/software-renderer-love2d)]

Space shooter. [[Source](https://github.com/agilul/spaceshooter-love2d)]
